{"tid":867553,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA 19 UT 討論區 (35) 又抽垃圾","createTime":"2018-10-18T18:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T01:14:03.000Z","uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d2424d9b8daead8341dfeda6900e93059d1c96","tid":867553,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家加入FIFA19 Ultimate Team討論區(ps3/ps4 ,xbox/xbox 1,pc,switch)&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開始前請先睇Q&amp;A，睇完搵唔到你想知既野先問，好多你想知既野都係第一版！拜託曬！&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFIFA UT web app:&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Fweb-app%2F&d=t4r4g0Dhr8wDwtQfLOx%2BfSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=14f420aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n球員資料database:&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://futhead.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffuthead.com&d=t4r4g0Dhr8wDwtQfLOx%2BfSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f613b683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://futhead.com</a>&amp;nbsp;[/url];<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://futwiz.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffutwiz.com&d=t4r4g0Dhr8wDwtQfLOx%2BfSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5fd382c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://futwiz.com</a>&amp;nbsp;[/url];<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSBC 答案 (參考idea, 抄足貴到仆街)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.futbin.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.futbin.com%2F&d=t4r4g0Dhr8wDwtQfLOx%2BfSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=2ddcb531\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.futbin.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFUT DATABASE&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/fut/database\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feasports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Ffut%2Fdatabase&d=t4r4g0Dhr8wDwtQfLOx%2BfSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8b71b93b\" target=\"_blank\">http://easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/fut/database</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n1.點樣可以contract 50%?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答:閃卡教練會加contract%, 金 3%銀 2%銅 1%, 普通金 1%, 總之最多50%,<br />\n買完個教練就咁store in club就可以加約。&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n2.係咪有金包送架?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答:係 game入面有張卡，其中一條係金包code<br />\n如果有, 係PS Store入面入code, 每星期就可以拎一包金包，記住唔係一次過拎晒<br />\n<br />\n3. 點賺錢?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答:踏實d, 打杯打比賽, 要快手就去淘寶課金, 切記今年EA&rdquo; 話&rdquo; 會嚴打買賣coins, 後果自負&amp;nbsp;<br />\n玩耐左可以試下炒卡。&amp;nbsp;<br />\n另外要留意賣卡會收「稅」，成功交易會抽5%，如賣10,000 coins成交，實收9,500&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n4. 咩係chemistry?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答:簡單d黎講, 高chemistry d隊員走位好d唔會成碌木咁唔走位, 另外個人chemistry會影響能力&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n5. 咁點加chemistry呀?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答:位置、球員之間既連線、教練、loyalty等等都會影響chemistry。&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n6. 咩係綠色連線?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答:球員同球員之間ge連線&amp;nbsp;<br />\n有3個原素&amp;nbsp;<br />\na.國籍 b.聯賽 c.球隊&amp;nbsp;<br />\n符合兩樣就夠, 咁樣有綠色連線&amp;nbsp;<br />\n一樣的話都有橙色&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n7. 咩係IF?咩係TOTW?點解有d卡會係黑色?<br />\n答:每星期三晚2點am都會有新既TOTW (team of the week)&amp;nbsp;<br />\n出既人會有張加強版既黑色卡，又叫IF (in form)&amp;nbsp;<br />\nNIF (not in form)係指有出過IF既人既普通版<br />\n黑卡因為多數只會出一個星期唔會再出，所以相當保值&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n8. 咩係happy hour? 點解有時會有d限數量既pack?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答:EA有時會出promo pack，如15,000 coins既premium jumbo pack&amp;nbsp;<br />\n有時一星期會有一兩個鐘既happy hour(唔知幾時先再有)，同有special promo pack之類，呢個係唔定時，視乎係咩種類既pack，可以抽5次或者10次，最貴既100K pack (24個全閃金球員)就只限抽一次&amp;nbsp;<br />\n要留意EASPORTSFIFA既twitter&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n9.chemistry style係咩黎?持續幾耐?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答: 唔同chemistry style會對球員某d 能力有唔同提升, 每個球員一開始都有basic呢個style&amp;nbsp;<br />\n你會見到每項能力都有一格V形箭嘴(假設chemistry 10), 唔代表果項能力 1&amp;nbsp;<br />\nchemistry style卡係永遠套用於某個球員, 直至你apply另一張落去&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n10: 隻Game 有無 handicap? 咩係handicap<br />\n答: 有handicap已經係公開o既秘密,而Handicap會令你經常有著數, 例如55波爭贏, 射門入球率大增&amp;nbsp;<br />\n而點先會令佢出現, 通常d人會透過壓星(壓Rating) 去令佢出現&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n11: 你地成日講H/H, H/M, M/L 係乜勁呀?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n答: 代表球員work rate, 分H-high, M-medium, L-low<br />\nH/H就則係個球員atk同def work rate都係high<br />\n<br />\n12: 乜野係ONE TO WATCH呢？<br />\n答: 就係呢個球員（球員A）今季先轉會，咁就有幸比FIFA觀察<br />\n屌 你見到果啲黑卡 有金邊果啲叫inform卡，if卡數值定死左，就算佢之後再有好表現，都係會再出一張新卡。你成張黑色果啲叫otw卡 係會跟inform卡 upgrade數值，咁你就唔洗次次都要買新卡囉，咁依家你隻bruma都未撚inform過，咁你張黑卡又點撚樣加能力姐 明唔撚明呀 臭雞<br />\n<br />\n13: SBC 點解跟網上嘅陣會唔夠CHEM? [FROM FIFA搏擊會]<br />\n答: 其實大家可以睇睇你班球員有無loyalty，因為抽返嚟嘅球員同踢過十場嘅球員都會有一點為上限嘅loyalty<br />\n刷loyalty方法：<br />\n開波，踢郁左個波之後，出去PS嘅設定，網絡入面測試網絡，如是者十場，又立即得，得咗！咁呢個方法就唔會計敗場，但會用多左時間！<br />\n<br />\n14: WEEKEND LEAGUE 點解打到金三都無下星期QUALIFY?<br />\n答: 下星期wl資格會係派彩時一同發放<br />\n<br />\n15:抽到xxxxxx應該賣定自用?<br />\n答: 我打機定你打機呀? 同三姑六婆問啲股票揸定沽有咩分別"},{"pid":"ace98eabdf3efadc7cac50466152c84adc305423","tid":867553,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DkBL9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DkBL9P.jpg&h=34d31f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1001唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb70613e07e1db389f333193cabc176148ac132","tid":867553,"uid":83172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace98eabdf3efadc7cac50466152c84adc305423","tid":867553,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DkBL9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DkBL9P.jpg&h=34d31f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1001唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:21:30.000Z","msg":"同時開 推返個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1fc398319237f3869e8ac9a5a89e0e9fcad4ff","tid":867553,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace98eabdf3efadc7cac50466152c84adc305423","tid":867553,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:20:49.0